inName)`** -- Returns the count of non-flagged reviews (`WHERE flagged = 0`) for the plugin.</result>\n<usage><total_tokens>14198</total_tokens><tool_uses>10</tool_uses><duration_ms>46058</duration_ms></usage>\n</task-notification>\nFull transcript available at: /tmp/claude-1000/-workspace/tasks/a5e7531ec2c39fab8.output"}
